Student > Course enrolment Requirements:

Admin / Course API:
*1. Admin wants to add / update a course
*2. See all students registered
*3. see all students registered to a course
API: GET:course/{course_id}/students

Student API:
*1. Student wants to register
*2. Wants to see all courses available
*3. Enroll to a course [by making payment]
API: student/{student_id}/course/{course_id}

Common API:
1. Enrolled courses by student id.
REST API[end point]: student/{student_id}/course